data.description:
Perched on the hill is an 1800 sqft Garrison style home overlooking the Kennebec River Valley. The home is on a slab with 3 bedrooms and two full baths.
Kitchen, dining room, den, full bath and sitting area on the first floor. Three bedrooms, living room area and full bath on the second. The interior has been updated with all new vinyl flooring, new paint and the kitchen and baths have been updated. There is a oversized 3 car detached garage with large room above for possible in-law apt or recreational room. One bay is tall enough for car lift. Garage has water, power and septic hooked up to it for future expansion. All new siding on the garage. Back on the market due to buyer qualification issues.
